author: Kuokka77
description:
"Roxy, I Like You" by Bartesek/Casyopea, 4th at Xenium 2025 tracked music compo.
Amiga art "Chalupy 2077" by .misha./Nah-Kolor^Tatanka, 2nd at Xenium 2025 oldschool gfx compo.

French CA4003290 Atari STe with new Mean Well RPD-60A PSU (SidecarTridge.com variety).
Playback using The Player v1.0 (advertises true 50 kHz replay, no multiplex or oversample cheating).

STe hardware has its issues, mine is not an exception. The infamous DAC whistle was removed using iZotope RX 6 spectral de-noiser. Crackling during DMA sound, while not 100% eliminated, got improved dramatically after applying Exxos STE DAC CRACKLES POP FIX (additional grounding for U500 and U501 via bodge wires).
title: STe does PT mod: Bartesek - Roxy, I Like You (STe🎧Dolbyfied)
